{"tid":1473040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［提防港豬心理陷阱］示威者要對生活受示威影響嘅市民道歉","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:17:27.000Z","uid":173326,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48303e2120a6c3a36e97170a55290344b1409ac3","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收皮啦！香港搞成咁入示威者數？<br />\n根本就完全100%係政府嘅責任！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係想攬示威者，而係示威者從開始到今都只係受害者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">根本就係政府做錯先，69遊行100萬人，個個都和平理性嘉年華式遊行，政府表示已經聽到市民聲音 。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢個時候政府順應民意徹底撤回、保證至少自己任內唔再推，就可以好似當年23條咁快速平息民怨，大家第二朝繼續做不問政治嘅港豬。<br />\n<br />\n但專橫跋扈嘅政府以612血腥暴力鎮壓作為回應，先搞到由反送中變成五大訴求。<br />\n因為大家612後就明白，撤回送中只係治標，結束呢個暴政制度先係治本（可以同一國兩制冇衝突）<br />\n<br />\n自612開始，政府縱容黑警唔跟守則做事，罔顧市民安全同合法權益，甚至不斷慫恿、包庇黑警掃射、虐打市民。<br />\n<br />\n淋病更加公開詆毀廣大市民對香港經濟嘅貢獻，藍絲用曱甴嚟形容所有不滿政府嘅人，企圖為黑警虐殺廣大街坊市民作心理鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n而家黑警有政府撐腰為所欲為，隨便用過分武力清場、使用私刑，晚晚各區tg橫飛亦波及本來中立嘅街坊，令香港變成無法無天嘅亂局。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>上述事實都反映，香港今日社會動盪嘅元兇同唯一要負責嘅人，只係呢個軍政府自己一個。</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個班覺得係示威者搞成香港咁、主張示威者道歉嘅人，我相信大部分只係誤墮港豬奴性心理陷阱，希望佢地理清前因後果。<br />\n<ins><strong>唔好見到示威者塞路就將塞路嘅責任歸咎示威者</strong></ins>，否則只會同港豬藍絲一樣。"},{"pid":"0e47f29134c66eb1c6498d51162998befc4a9667","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"因為A被B打左一棍，A成面血滴落地面，跟住中立嘅C路過俾啲血冼親。<br />\n<br />\nB連同中立嘅C去指責A整污糟地下？<br />\n甚至A自己都覺得自己有責任，要對C道歉？<br />\n<br />\n唔好講笑喇，屌哂ABC你地老母！"},{"pid":"d212afbf7bf31297f8677470d042eaff8a210e36","tid":1473040,"uid":295889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472905</a><br />\n<br />\n其實真係有需要set deadline（已經有唔少共識） <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">太家幫手投一投票</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b95084dc0c9c7d000fe905e2737204e97f2afb4","tid":1473040,"uid":295218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aejBkFU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aejBkFU</a>"},{"pid":"e2f142a57048d7b823e22ee98ce5a1a9d7415998","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:59:58.000Z","msg":"堅持道歉個啲唔該話俾我知，示威者到底有乜做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817ec232bfe5c172a7833e39be0363e942d0aad5","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:36:55.000Z","msg":"雖然示威者繼續做港豬忍受暴政煮蛙嘅話，香港今日唔會咁亂咁多流血，但如果政府聽到、肯聽民意嘅話，香港社會民生會有好大改善<br />\n<br />\n而目前如果示威者放棄嘅話，邊個向6條人命同受傷義士道歉？邊個向受政治打壓嘅下一代道歉？邊個向自己um實嘅良心道歉？"},{"pid":"3355ac1271a052397d94d339f1ab6e146bf76c42","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbaa0448f06ff0d0b7d069c72fc6fa918b79a7f","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f20795c90df1ba915ae0d77973770b0a6feac9","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"快啲醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4535f8d6ecd9b71cff26c9677d0d2413da40f903","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e47f29134c66eb1c6498d51162998befc4a9667","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"因為A被B打左一棍，A成面血滴落地面，跟住中立嘅C路過俾啲血冼親。<br />\n<br />\nB連同中立嘅C去指責A整污糟地下？<br />\n甚至A自己都覺得自己有責任，要對C道歉？<br />\n<br />\n唔好講笑喇，屌哂ABC你地老母！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"廣大市民平日已經俾政府長期壓迫，而政府得寸進尺，想用送中惡法去被消失所有異見人士<br />\n<br />\n部分異見人士發現大禍臨頭，就6月9出嚟合法和平咁遊行啦，點知政府嘅回應只係612暴力鎮壓，甚至對之後嘅所有合法活動直接開槍清場（包括有不反對通知書嘅遊行集會、民間路邊安全燒衣）<br />\n<br />\n有人不滿政府處理手法，於是企出嚟批評政府、要求交代。<br />\n呢個時候政府同藍絲就批評呢班不滿嘅人係搞亂香港、影響廣大市民。<br />\n而最慘嘅係呢班表達不滿嘅市民，居然有部分真係覺得自己有錯，甚至覺得要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d138ff6386e83c478de62ee7b4f2877c1534850b","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:40:47.000Z","msg":"黑警非法毆打市民，其他市民上前驅趕黑警嚟救人，咁市民係咪要向個黑警道歉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685e08f6486a115064be97010cc1a455cde40ffe","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"責任根本唔在於表達不滿嘅人，而係在於造成不滿嘅人"},{"pid":"91ebd31243ef6e9b1dbbe53a9e387f9c7b741b4b","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔好因為政府唔認錯，所以自己去承擔政府嘅錯"},{"pid":"1b6701c86902cfcb366045a24a57169290cfc8d7","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"政府主動抹黑異見人士係預左，但估唔到真係有人爭住認啲唔屬於自己嘅錯"},{"pid":"4b977b87fe27ef4110a9b71b24d999f14d87bef0","tid":1473040,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:17:27.000Z","msg":"呢張圖真係精闢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nnimgt-a.akamaihd.net/transform/v1/crop/frm/kDqE8LvSwvU8fyZkrZC97F/e314e174-5205-4f87-9aec-915a90e9e044.jpg/r0_0_1024_675_w1200_h678_fmax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnnimgt-a.akamaihd.net%2Ftransform%2Fv1%2Fcrop%2Ffrm%2FkDqE8LvSwvU8fyZkrZC97F%2Fe314e174-5205-4f87-9aec-915a90e9e044.jpg%2Fr0_0_1024_675_w1200_h678_fmax.jpg&h=a21df75b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}